    fsump1fi.3 $e |- ( x e. B -> A. k x e. B ) $.
    fsump1fi.4 $e |- ( k = ( N + 1 ) -> A = B ) $.
    $( The addition of the next term in a finite sum of ` A ( k ) ` is the
       previous term plus ` A ( N + 1 ) = B ` . $)
